 How to Register
 ===============

Skimmer is shareware. Please support the shareware concept! If you find this
program to be of value to you, consider registering it. Besides giving me a
warm fuzzy for a job well done, it will encourage me to do more nifty tools
for the Amiga. I see this as a "good thing." :-)

Registration is $10.00 US, 7 UKP in the UK. Any bugfix releases are of
