@node "Bugs" " Bugs         "
 Known Bugs and how you can help
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 As of this writing, only two minor bugs are known to exist.

 o If the registration process is aborted for some reason, then Skimmer
   instructed to start a scan, multi-assigned LIBS: dir may not be
   fully delved.

 o If you're using a language other than English, the hotkeys don't
   make much sense. This is because the hotkeys are hard-coded. This
   will be fixed in V2.

Of course, also send bug reports of unrelated bugs that might have slipped
past the beta testers. They're a sharp bunch, though :-)

Send bug reports to dlg@maximumaccess.com.

